<br>
 On aggro I found the best way to die against a high HP summoning creature is to snare, then heal the cleric it is currently beating on because of over aggroing healing. I would always prefer for a Ranger to snare duing a big encounter because snaring then chain healing to keep someone alive will almost always get me summoned and then usually killed. It seems if I am just aggro from the heals and not from snaring usually they can taunt it off before I die. <br>
<br>
Aelwr 55th Druid <br>
